Name: First Floor
About the game: In this first person game you start off on the third floor of a storage facility and need to escape. Search for keys on the floor you are on to open the locked door of that floor and get to the next floor. Once on the first floor you'll need to find the key to unlock the exit so you can escape. Be careful as you search though as there may be a monster stalking you.
